snippet.title: Lego Friends Pop Star Show Stage Set Unboxing Building Review - Kids Toys
snippet.description:
Lego Friends Pop Star Show Stage Set 41105, released mid-2015, is a cute modular set, all ready for the Lego Friends girls to roleplay being popstars with Livi! The runways can be rearranged to suit you, and there is a keyboard, electric guitar and drum kit included too. My favourite feature on this set is by far the internal workings of gears and cogs that make parts of the stage spin - this set is for older kids - and I love the incorporation of Technic pieces into the building. 

Put on a spectacular show with LEGO® Friends!

Get set for a show-stopping performance with Livi the pop star! The incredible stage is set for tonight’s concert. As the show starts, turn the stage panels to make Livi appear as if from nowhere. Set Andrea up on the drums or at the keyboard to accompany Livi for the first songs. Then it’s time for the highlight of the show—Livi sings her hit single while Andrea plays the electric guitar like a pro. Use the dancing function to see their slick dance moves! Now it’s time to rearrange the stage while Livi has a costume change before her big finale. This has been Livi’s best show yet! Includes Livi the pop star and Andrea mini-doll figures.

Includes Livi the pop star and Andrea mini-doll figures
Features a modular stage with catwalk, big screen, background panels, brick-built speakers, pop star reveal function, dancing function, drums and a keyboard set
Accessory elements include 2 fabric skirts, microphone, drumsticks and a guitar
Rearrange the different parts of the stage to create the perfect set
Turn the panels to create a magical pop star entrance
Put on the ultimate pop star spectacular with music and dance
Choose different outfits for Livi and Andrea to wear on stage

snippet.title: LEGO Disney Princess Sleeping Beauty's Royal Bedroom Unboxing Building and Play 2015 - Kids Toys
snippet.description:
Join me to build Aurora's Royal Bedroom (sped up a bit so it's not too dull when I'm trying to find the pieces that drop on the floor). It's utterly charming with a princess bed (with hidden cache underneath), a window seat, dressing table and the famous spinning wheel and dreaded spindle! Oh, and a bunny. Because of course Sleeping Beauty has to have a weeny white rabbit for a pet. And the bunny comes in handy at the end, take a look and see, the story goes just a little differently to the Disney version. ;)

snippet.title: LEGO Friends Heartlake City Hair Salon (41391) - Toy Unboxing and Speed Build
snippet.description:
Heartlake City Hair Salon

Item: 41391
Ages: 6+
Pieces: 235

Where better to meet up with friends and share a gossip than at the salon? This toy hair styling set is brimming with scenarios for imaginative play. There’s a whole host of cute hairdressing toy salon accessories, such as toy hair dryers and toy wigs, to get imaginations sparking. With LEGO® Friends Heartlake City Hair Salon (41391) kids can role-play the client or the stylist – there's loads of crazy cuts waiting to be made. Action stations Wonderfully detailed stations allow kids to see the mini-doll figures progress through the pretend hair salon. Cute features include a shell-shaped sink, a hair-cutting chair, a styling station and a cash register. Purple bangs anyone? Instructions volumized All LEGO sets come with super-simple printed instructions, but the Heartlake City Hair Salon also features a fully enhanced building experience. Download the LEGO Life app and go to Instructions PLUS to access zoom, rotate and ‘ghost' modes. It's building for the digital age!
- Give little stylists hours of creative play with LEGO® Friends Heartlake City Hair Salon. They can pretend to cut and style their friends’ hair or imagine they are the client going to the play hair salon for a new do!
- The set is packed with features to get imaginations firing. There are 2 mini-dolls, 2 hairdressing chairs, a hair-washing sink and lots of accessories, such as toy brushes and toy wigs, to create a realistic salon experience.
- Kids will have loads of fun watching the mini-doll figure’s transformation as she progresses through the stations of the salon. And to ramp up the fun they can make over the minifigures from any other LEGO® set too!
- With 235 pieces, Heartlake City Hair Salon (41391) is an ideal gift for kids with a little building experience and a lot of imagination. It makes a great birthday, holiday or special-occasion gift for kids aged 6 and up.
- Measuring just over 4” (11cm) high and 6” (17cm) long, this play hair salon is compact enough to keep ondisplay for constant entertainment. Or kids can combine it with other LEGO® sets for truly creative play.
- No batteries are needed to power up the Heartlake City Hair Salon. The creative fun comes alive with a simple set of instructions, a little building experience and a child's active imagination.
- Is your little builder ready for an awesome play experience? Download the LEGO® Life app and help them use Instructions PLUS to see their hair salon in zoom, rotate and ‘ghost' modes. It's building for the digital age!
- Introduce little builders to the world of Heartlake City, where the girls from LEGO® Friends are waiting to accompany them on their imagination’s most exciting adventures!
- LEGO® sets meet the highest industry standards plus The LEGO Group's own quality criteria. They're consistent, compatible and connect and pull apart easily every time – it's been that way since 1958.
- LEGO® Friends sets, bricks and accessories are tested to the max to ensure that every LEGO toy playset meets the highest global safety and quality standards.

source: LEGO

snippet.title: Lego Friends Heartlake Grand Hotel Set Unboxing Building Review Part Two  - Kids Toys
snippet.description:
Lego Friends Heartlake Grand Hotel Set 41101 is a ginormous set, the box is very heavy. This is a speed build with slow parts to really look at each room as it is made - there is so much detail to see! The set is huge so even with a speed build I needed to split it into two - this is the second half, here's the link to the first half http://bit.ly/2bKIuum

This has got to be the biggest Lego Friends set yet, it's at least twice the size of Olivia's or Emma's House. There are lots of details in this set, with five mini dolls - Olivia, Nate, Andrea, Stephanie and Andrea's Mum Susan who runs the hotel. Three levels with a working elevator, revolving door, hotel cafe and lobby, black taxi, jazz lounge with saxophone and grand piano and microphone, rooftop pool with dj area, two guest bedrooms - the list goes on and on and I can't think of everything!

snippet.title: Lego Friends Pop Star Dressing Room Set Unboxing Building Review - Kids Toys
snippet.description:
Lego Friends Pop Star Dressing Room 41104 released mid-2015 features pop star Livi and Lego Friends Emma who comes along to style her over before her concert. I couldn't go past this set - Livi has pink and blue hair and three sparkly skirts to mix and match with. Plus her little dalmation puppy Cookie has got music notes mixed in with his spots. So very cute! The dressing room is hinged so you can set it up in all sorts of different ways. Check out the specs below and let me know what your favourite part of the set is!

Get glammed up in the foldout Pop Star Dressing Room! Livi the pop star has a big show tonight and Emma is her stylist. Help Emma choose an amazing outfit for Livi to wear on stage, then sit Livi down at the vanity desk to have her hair done. Which style and accessories will you choose tonight?

Then it’s time to relax before the performance. Fold the dressing room back to create a special doggy pampering area for Livi’s Dalmatian, Cookie. Put him in his doggy bed with a bone while Livi sits on the sofa to read some fan mail. The show is about to start, so put the finishing touches to Livi’s makeover, take a glamorous fabric skirt from the hangers and dress Livi with it. Now, she really looks like a superstar!

Includes Livi the pop star and Emma mini-doll figures, plus Cookie the Dalmatian
Folds out to create different areas with a mirrored vanity desk and clothes rail with fabric skirts
Tilting full-length mirror, sofa, opening mini-fridge element, functioning mailbox and a doggy bed
Accessories include electric blue and pink wigs, 3 fabric skirts, flowers, fan mail, fruit, bottle, magazine and a bone for Cookie
Combine with the Lego Friends Pop Star Stage (41105) to create the whole concert experience (sold separately)
279 pieces
Pop Star Dressing Room: 10 (h) x 38 (w) x 9 (d) cm

snippet.title: Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz  Unboxing and  Review Kids Toys  Kyrascope
snippet.description:
Our magical sun gives gardens and farms the light and warmth they need to grow the ingredients that go into all our favourite foods. Kyra's unboxing the super fun Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz experiment kit to show you how food grows!

Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz: Grow Your Garden, Grow Your Learning

Plants are magic. They give us oxygen to breathe, and they give us delicious food and fruits to eat.

Kyra is learning the science behind the magic with the help of her new Garden Sciencz Experimental Educational Game by Piramal Healthcare's Jungle Magic series for kids. She has donned her lab coat, and her thinking cap as she learns step by step the processes that go into planting a seed, making it sprout and nurturing it into a fully grown plant.

What is more, now that Kyra knows how important different types of soil are she is also closely observing all the different muds of India wherever she goes, which means a lot more dirt on her hands and shoes! But her parents don't mind so much. She is getting closer to nature after all.  

The Garden Sciencz kit contains 20 different experiments in growing plants, soil samples, and different types of seeds of food crops like wheat, coriander, mustard, fenugreek and many more. Kyra is eagerly waiting for her "food to start growing" on her plants, she checks on them every five minutes! If you have a curious little person in your life, we suggest you get them this kit too to arouse some hunger for observing nature as well as appreciation for patient practice of gardening.

About the Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz kit by Piramal Healthcare

Suitable for ages 7 and above, this kit contains an instruction manual with an introduction to different Indian soils and crops and a detailed guide to growing plants. It contains everything the child will need to grow their own plant, except for water. All material used is environment friendly.


Best Buy Link : https://amzn.to/2LOmSiY

Give your kids a fun learning experience

Kit contains environment friendly parts, detailed easy to understand step-by-step instruction manual, colors and learning materials

Suitable for: Age 7 years old and above

Jungle Magic is a renowned Brand of Piramal Healthcare, Provides safe, high quality creative toys and games for boys n girls

Basics of Botany science

Greenhouse effect

snippet.title: Rusty Rivets Botasaur Dinosaur Spin Master Toy Unboxing Review || Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:
Combine it and design it with Rusty Rivets! Now you can bring Rusty’s iconic dinosaur to life with Botasaur. Use the tools and parts included in this set to create rustified fun! Once built, this dinosaur can transform into a vehicle for hours of imaginative and creative play!

This easy-to-build set allows kids to combine it and design it just like Rusty! Rusty fans will develop their logic, building and fine motor skills as they assemble the parts of the Botasaur. Once created, kids can let their imagination run wild as they play with their favorite dinosaur!

A Rusty Rivets unboxing, demo and review by Keith's Toy Box.

Click here for more Rusty Rivets Toys:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfUxTWckfQK2Hsmfwd6bECELOHfZvjOII

RUSTY RIVETS Complete Toys from Spin Master Rivet Lab, Botasaur || Keith's Toy Box
https://youtu.be/583gnDKKDE4

Rusty Rivets is a Canadian CGI interactive animated television series produced by Arc Productions and Spin Master Entertainment for Treehouse TV and Nickelodeon Productions. Inspired by elements of the maker culture, it follows the adventures of a young inventor named Rusty and his team of customized robots. A boy named Rusty Rivets uses his knowledge of engineering to repurpose machine parts and create gadgets. He lives in the city of Sparkton Hills along with his friend Ruby Ramirez, a robotic tyrannosaurid named Botasaur, and a group of smaller robots known as the Bits. The show highlights a variety of concepts related to basic science and technology.

Rusty uses the recurring catch phrase "modify, customize, Rustify" when personalizing inventions. Ruby changes the last word to "Rubify" when she does the alterations.


=========================================

snippet.title: LEGO Chima Maula's Ice Mammoth Stomper 70145 Kids Toy Review & Unboxing
snippet.description:
LEGO Chima Maula's Ice Mammoth Stomper 70145 Kids Toy Review & Unboxing

The icy bad guys from the Mammoth and Saber-tooth tribes are getting away with the CHI in Maula’s Ice Mammoth Stomper. With a weapon in its trunk plus 2 ice blaster cannons and hidden flick missiles, this is one fearsome armored vehicle. snippet.title: RC4WD Unboxing & RC First Run  - RTR 4WD Realistic RC Truck
snippet.description:
You know how we do it - straight up unbox and run! This RC4WD Desert Runner RTR 4WD Scale Truck w/Hero Body & 2.4GHz Radio (Black) is a realistic RC truck that can still do a little crawling and bashing!  We give our honest RC first impressions as we RC Unbox and give an RC toy review on this new 1/10 scale RC trophy truck and take it on its RC First Run.  We love this RC toys unboxing, because of all of our RC trucks, this RC4WD Hero is the most RC scale truck we own so far.  

This RC4WD scale truck features a hard plastic body, chassis mounted servo, independent front suspension, a leaf sprung solid rear axle, full interior and remote locking front and rear differentials. This off road truck has other features like reservoir shocks, functional light buckets, and a full interior with complete dash assembly and more.  Lucky for us, this RC4WD Ford Raptor truck is RTR with electronics pre-installed - so batteries in and ride!!

snippet.title: Hand Controlled Flying Saucer UFO w IR and LED Lights - Unboxing Demo Review
snippet.description:
It's so easy to fly this Hand-Controlled Flying Saucer UFO with Infrared (IR) and LED Lights!  Just wave your hand under it to make it fly, no need for a remote control!  It works by infrared (IR) technology that detects any surface below it and makes it hover and rise up!  It has a foam body that lets it withstand falls, crashes, or bounce of walls!  Its flashing LED lights makes it really COOL to fly at night! Other than just your hand, you can also try more advanced tricks like using your legs, knees, arms or shoulders!  Use the catching stick to play catch with friends and toss it back and forth!    Similar to Vectron Wave or Air Hogs or Air Eagle UFO Flyers
- Easy-to-fly hand-controlled Flying Saucer, UFO, perfect for beginners, no need for remote control
- Works by Infrared (IR) technology that detects any surface and makes it hover and rise up!
- Foam body lets it withstand falls and crashes, or lets it bounce of walls!
- Flashing LED lights make it really cool to fly at night!
- Other than your hand, you can also use your legs, knees, arms or shoulders!
- Play catch with friends and toss it back and forth with the use of the catching stick!
- Comes with USB charging cable and built-in rechargeable lithium batteries, charge for 20 minutes, good for 3-7 minutes of flying time.
- Fly indoors or outdoors, but keep away from people's faces, eyes, animals, and fragile objects.

Available at Banggood here:
http://www.banggood.com/Flying-Saucer-UFO-Hand-Induced-Hovering-And-Floating-Flight-With-LED-p-962129.html?utm_source=panxiaohong&utm_medium=Keith&utm_campaign=panxiaohong

snippet.title: The Baa-Baa Barn from John Crane Unboxing & Toy Review
snippet.description:
In this episode of the Fun Kids Toy Club, presenters Bex and Sean are unboxing the Baa-Baa Barn from John Crane Ltd and giving their toy review.

This toy is a big old barn with loads of different farm animals like a cow, horse, sheep, pig, a little rabbit and quite a few other animals too as Bex discovers!

Sean also gets very excited when he finds out that when the animals head into the barn they break into song!

Although Sean also shows why you should never trust him with ANY toy, not even one made for children aged 2 years plus!

You can find out more about the children's radio station, Fun Kids at http://www.funkidslive.com
